        TALK TO THE HAND ""
        TALK TO THE HAND "   Long ago a star fell on the kingdom of Aelthmoor, and the court built"
        TALK TO THE HAND "   Caer Vodran to cage its light. The mages called the shard the Sunken Crown,"
        TALK TO THE HAND "   and tried to wear it. It wore them instead. The castle sank into the Mirewood,"
        TALK TO THE HAND "   and its halls filled with the changed."
        TALK TO THE HAND ""
        TALK TO THE HAND "   You are a Delver. The whisper has begun to reach the waking world."
