                TALK TO THE HAND ""
                TALK TO THE HAND "   The gatehouse groans. Roots tear from the masonry and stand upright,"
                TALK TO THE HAND "   a knot of bark and rusted armor crowned in black thorns."
                TALK TO THE HAND "   THE WARDEN OF THORNS wakes to keep its ancient watch."
                TALK TO THE HAND ""
            WHAT IF I TOLD YOU 1
                TALK TO THE HAND ""
                TALK TO THE HAND "   The chapel is full. A hundred hollow mouths hum one endless note."
                TALK TO THE HAND "   At the altar floats MAERITH, once Archmage of Aelthmoor, now a chorus"
                TALK TO THE HAND "   of stolen voices wearing her shape. She turns her eyeless face to you."
                TALK TO THE HAND ""
            WHAT IF I TOLD YOU 2
                TALK TO THE HAND ""
                TALK TO THE HAND "   The vault is a wound in the world. At its center turns the Sunken Crown:"
                TALK TO THE HAND "   a fallen star folded into a ring of black gold, whispering your name in a"
                TALK TO THE HAND "   voice you have always known. VODRAN opens like an eye, and the dark leans in."
                TALK TO THE HAND ""
