                        TALK TO THE HAND "   Beneath the altar, a stair descends toward a buried star."
                    WHAT IF I TOLD YOU 2
                        TALK TO THE HAND "   You drive the final blow into the heart of the star. The whisper"
                        TALK TO THE HAND "   stutters, climbs to a shriek - and goes out, like a candle pinched cold."
                        TALK TO THE HAND "   The Mirewood exhales. Far above, for the first time in an age, it is morning."
